WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.667 --> 00:00:02.585
Tonight, a senior Hamas leader is dead

00:00:02.585 --> 00:00:03.795
amid serious concerns

00:00:03.795 --> 00:00:05.171
the war in the Middle East

00:00:05.171 --> 00:00:06.256
is about to get bigger.

00:00:06.256 --> 00:00:08.049
Salah al-Hariri, a top official

00:00:08.049 --> 00:00:10.176
in Hamas's military and political wings,

00:00:10.176 --> 00:00:11.344
killed in Beirut.

00:00:11.344 --> 00:00:12.595
Hamas says the leader was killed

00:00:12.595 --> 00:00:13.722
by an Israeli airstrike.

00:00:13.722 --> 00:00:14.806
Israel, however,

00:00:14.806 --> 00:00:17.017
is not taking responsibility.

00:00:17.017 --> 00:00:18.101
And this is all happening

00:00:18.101 --> 00:00:19.269
as Iran has dispatched

00:00:19.269 --> 00:00:21.229
a naval destroyer to the Red Sea.

00:00:21.229 --> 00:00:22.731
Tensions there escalating

00:00:22.731 --> 00:00:24.149
following a series of attacks

00:00:24.149 --> 00:00:26.317
by the Iranian backed Houthi militia,

00:00:26.317 --> 00:00:28.361
including against the United States.

00:00:28.528 --> 00:00:30.280
And now the US Navy has killed Houthis

00:00:30.280 --> 00:00:31.239
for the first time

00:00:31.239 --> 00:00:32.907
since this conflict broke out,

00:00:32.907 --> 00:00:33.742
sinking three

00:00:33.742 --> 00:00:35.368
the boots at boats, rather,

00:00:35.368 --> 00:00:37.328
after being attacked in the Red Sea

00:00:37.328 --> 00:00:38.455
this weekend.

00:00:38.455 --> 00:00:40.206
Oren Liebermann is OUTFRONT tonight.

00:00:40.206 --> 00:00:40.957
At war in the U.S.

00:00:40.957 --> 00:00:42.584
really getting drawn further

00:00:42.584 --> 00:00:44.335
and further into this conflict.

00:00:44.335 --> 00:00:46.755
Iranian involvement clearly evident.

00:00:47.338 --> 00:00:49.049
What is the U.S. going to do next?

00:00:50.008 --> 00:00:50.425
Eric, the

00:00:50.425 --> 00:00:51.676
Biden administration's

00:00:51.676 --> 00:00:52.218
position is

00:00:52.218 --> 00:00:52.635
they don't

00:00:52.635 --> 00:00:54.345
want to see a regional escalation.

00:00:54.345 --> 00:00:54.763
They don't want to see

00:00:54.763 --> 00:00:56.264
a widening of the war.

00:00:56.264 --> 00:00:58.224
But clearly, it's not just up to the U.S.

00:00:58.224 --> 00:00:59.684
to make a unilateral decision

00:00:59.684 --> 00:01:00.518
in this case.

00:01:00.518 --> 00:01:01.478
The events we've seen over

00:01:01.478 --> 00:01:03.188
the course of the past couple of days

00:01:03.188 --> 00:01:05.231
make a widening of the war,

00:01:05.231 --> 00:01:07.233
an escalation, a growing possibility,

00:01:07.317 --> 00:01:08.318
not only, as you pointed out

00:01:08.318 --> 00:01:09.402
over the weekend,

00:01:09.402 --> 00:01:10.779
the US military and U.S.

00:01:10.779 --> 00:01:12.155
attack helicopters sinking

00:01:12.155 --> 00:01:14.115
three fast attack boats

00:01:14.115 --> 00:01:14.616
that were going

00:01:14.616 --> 00:01:15.825
after a commercial vessel

00:01:15.825 --> 00:01:17.535
and killing the cruise of those

00:01:17.535 --> 00:01:18.661
for the first time

00:01:18.661 --> 00:01:19.537
since the war,

00:01:19.537 --> 00:01:20.121
but also

00:01:20.121 --> 00:01:21.831
now the killing of such a brewery,

00:01:21.831 --> 00:01:24.626
a senior Hamas militant in Beirut.

00:01:24.793 --> 00:01:26.961
So the US has to watch all of this.

00:01:27.003 --> 00:01:27.337
The U.S.

00:01:27.337 --> 00:01:28.254
does have the backing

00:01:28.254 --> 00:01:29.506
of an international coalition

00:01:29.506 --> 00:01:30.173
in the Red Sea,

00:01:30.173 --> 00:01:31.716
and that gives it essentially

00:01:31.716 --> 00:01:33.760
some weight here in its actions. The U.S.

00:01:33.760 --> 00:01:35.970
monitoring that Iranian Navy vessel

00:01:35.970 --> 00:01:37.597
that's in the Red Sea from the U.S.

00:01:37.597 --> 00:01:38.306
is a position.

00:01:38.306 --> 00:01:39.933
It is an international waterway,

00:01:39.933 --> 00:01:41.142
a critical one

00:01:41.142 --> 00:01:42.852
that so they're allowed to be there.

00:01:42.852 --> 00:01:43.269
But the U.S.

00:01:43.269 --> 00:01:44.771
military will keep a very close

00:01:44.771 --> 00:01:45.563
eye on them

00:01:45.563 --> 00:01:47.857
as it watches where this all goes.

00:01:48.108 --> 00:01:49.275
For the killing of Saleh

00:01:49.275 --> 00:01:50.568
al-Hariri, who you saw there

00:01:50.568 --> 00:01:52.821
with the Ayatollah, the leader of Iran.

00:01:53.321 --> 00:01:54.447
We've seen promises

00:01:54.447 --> 00:01:55.240
of revenge

00:01:55.240 --> 00:01:56.199
and condemnation

00:01:56.199 --> 00:01:58.326
from the Iranians, from Hamas,

00:01:58.326 --> 00:02:00.286
Hezbollah and even some others.

00:02:00.286 --> 00:02:00.745
The question

00:02:00.745 --> 00:02:02.247
now, of course, what do they do?

00:02:02.247 --> 00:02:03.623
And they have a number of options.

00:02:03.623 --> 00:02:06.000
All of these Iranian proxies attack U.S.

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:07.752
forces in Iraq and Syria.

00:02:07.752 --> 00:02:08.503
Go after U.S.

00:02:08.503 --> 00:02:10.088
vessels in the Red Sea with the Houthis

00:02:10.088 --> 00:02:12.382
there from Yemen, attack Israel.

00:02:12.382 --> 00:02:13.424
Iran doesn't really see

00:02:13.424 --> 00:02:14.968
much of a difference between the U.S.

00:02:14.968 --> 00:02:15.635
and Israel.

00:02:15.635 --> 00:02:17.595
So this is all possibilities

00:02:17.595 --> 00:02:18.763
that we have to watch out for

00:02:18.763 --> 00:02:20.765
and that the U.S. is watching out for.

00:02:20.807 --> 00:02:21.641
Now, as you know,

00:02:21.641 --> 00:02:22.267
Israel hasn't

00:02:22.267 --> 00:02:23.852
officially taken responsibility

00:02:23.852 --> 00:02:24.769
for the killing of Salah

00:02:24.769 --> 00:02:26.146
al-Hariri in Beirut.

00:02:26.146 --> 00:02:26.855
Israeli officials

00:02:26.855 --> 00:02:28.606
have been a bit coy about this,

00:02:28.606 --> 00:02:29.858
but it is worth pointing to this

00:02:29.858 --> 00:02:31.484
tweet from Danny Danon,

00:02:31.484 --> 00:02:32.694
a current member of Knesset

00:02:32.694 --> 00:02:33.611
and the former Israeli

00:02:33.611 --> 00:02:35.113
ambassador to the U.N..

00:02:35.113 --> 00:02:36.281
He said on Twitter,

00:02:36.281 --> 00:02:37.073
I congratulate

00:02:37.073 --> 00:02:38.700
the IDF, the Shin Bet, the Mossad

00:02:38.700 --> 00:02:40.285
and the security forces for killing

00:02:40.285 --> 00:02:41.703
senior Hamas official Salah

00:02:41.703 --> 00:02:43.121
al-Hariri in Beirut.

00:02:43.121 --> 00:02:44.164
Anyone who was involved

00:02:44.164 --> 00:02:45.373
in the October 7th

00:02:45.373 --> 00:02:46.124
massacre should know

00:02:46.124 --> 00:02:46.833
that we will reach them

00:02:46.833 --> 00:02:48.042
and settle the account with them.

00:02:48.042 --> 00:02:49.669
So Eric are pretty clear there.

00:02:49.669 --> 00:02:50.170
It's also worth

00:02:50.170 --> 00:02:51.546
remembering that Benjamin Netanyahu

00:02:51.546 --> 00:02:52.630
promised Israel would go

00:02:52.630 --> 00:02:54.591
after Hamas leaders wherever they are.

00:02:54.591 --> 00:02:55.758
Yeah, that's for sure.

00:02:55.758 --> 00:02:56.968
And appreciate the reporting as always.

00:02:56.968 --> 00:02:57.427
Thank you.

