00:03:24.078 --> 00:03:25.205
that the Biden administration

00:03:25.205 --> 00:03:26.331
has been worried about.

00:03:26.331 --> 00:03:27.749
They have been trying to repress

00:03:27.749 --> 00:03:30.043
any kind of expansion of this conflict.

00:03:30.043 --> 00:03:32.712
And this strike in Beirut against

00:03:32.712 --> 00:03:33.963
the Hamas leader is

00:03:33.963 --> 00:03:36.216
is not going to help that at all.

00:03:36.216 --> 00:03:37.300
You also have to consider

00:03:37.300 --> 00:03:39.052
that the Hezbollah leader,

00:03:39.052 --> 00:03:40.470
Nasrallah, has said

00:03:40.470 --> 00:03:41.346
that any strikes

00:03:41.346 --> 00:03:43.723
inside of Lebanon by Israel,

00:03:43.723 --> 00:03:45.058
especially in Beirut,

00:03:45.058 --> 00:03:46.434
will cause serious

00:03:46.434 --> 00:03:48.186
repercussions for the Israelis.

00:03:48.186 --> 00:03:49.687
This is the Hezbollah leader.

00:03:49.687 --> 00:03:51.898
What Israel has been trying to do

00:03:51.898 --> 00:03:53.650
is not allow this

00:03:53.650 --> 00:03:55.818
to come into a multi-front war

00:03:55.818 --> 00:03:57.070
but we're already seeing that

00:03:57.070 --> 00:03:58.988
they are fighting hard in Gaza.

