the Maersk

00:05:00.466 --> 00:05:02.635
carrier the other day is an indicator

00:05:02.635 --> 00:05:04.304
of what the Iranians are attempting

00:05:04.304 --> 00:05:05.013
to do

00:05:05.013 --> 00:05:07.056
