We know at least five

00:05:38.046 --> 00:05:40.298
people killed today, at least 53.

00:05:40.298 --> 00:05:41.090
The number stands out

00:05:41.090 --> 00:05:43.426
now killed from Friday's massive attacks.

00:05:43.426 --> 00:05:45.136
We are nearly two years

00:05:45.136 --> 00:05:47.180
now into this war.

00:05:47.180 --> 00:05:48.306
How do you read the message

00:05:48.306 --> 00:05:50.516
that Putin is sending to Ukraine?

00:05:50.516 --> 00:05:50.808
Well,

00:05:50.808 --> 00:05:51.309
first of all,

00:05:51.309 --> 00:05:52.810
from the tactical perspective,

00:05:52.810 --> 00:05:54.395
what Russia has been trying to do

00:05:54.395 --> 00:05:56.230
is I use a basketball term,

00:05:56.230 --> 00:05:57.523
flood the zone.

00:05:57.523 --> 00:05:59.150
They are trying to put as many missiles

00:05:59.150 --> 00:06:00.777
in the air as they can.

00:06:00.777 --> 00:06:02.236
And there are all different types

00:06:02.236 --> 00:06:03.863
coming from multiple directions

00:06:03.863 --> 00:06:04.447
and multiple

00:06:04.447 --> 00:06:06.616
platforms, air, sea and ground.

00:06:07.450 --> 00:06:10.453
They are some of the types of missiles.

00:06:10.953 --> 00:06:12.246
The hypersonic

00:06:12.246 --> 00:06:14.415
missiles are very advanced.

00:06:14.916 --> 00:06:16.959
But Ukraine has been very successful

00:06:16.959 --> 00:06:18.586
in shooting most of them down.

00:06:18.586 --> 00:06:19.629
Today's

00:06:19.629 --> 00:06:22.006
activity, Ukraine was very successful.

00:06:22.298 --> 00:06:23.716
But what I would say is two

00:06:23.716 --> 00:06:24.425
things are happening.

00:06:24.425 --> 00:06:26.677
First of all, Russia is continuing

00:06:26.677 --> 00:06:28.388
their strategic approach

00:06:28.388 --> 00:06:29.555
to try and affect

00:06:29.555 --> 00:06:32.975
Ukrainian infrastructure to make it

00:06:32.975 --> 00:06:35.144
a harsh winter for Ukrainian citizens

00:06:35.144 --> 00:06:36.521
to continue to say,

00:06:36.521 --> 00:06:37.814
even though the United States

00:06:37.814 --> 00:06:39.482
and others may be balking,

00:06:39.482 --> 00:06:41.692
we're still going to attack. Great.

00:06:41.984 --> 00:06:42.944
And what's happening from

00:06:42.944 --> 00:06:44.320
the Ukrainian side

00:06:44.320 --> 00:06:45.613
is they just don't have

00:06:45.613 --> 00:06:47.865
enough air defense to cover everything,

00:06:48.074 --> 00:06:50.076
you know, air defense or points weapon

00:06:50.076 --> 00:06:51.244
systems, Erica.

00:06:51.244 --> 00:06:52.495
That means they have to be placed

00:06:52.495 --> 00:06:54.789
in a location to guard a specific target.

00:06:54.997 --> 00:06:56.165
So that means you can't

00:06:56.165 --> 00:06:57.625
defend everywhere.

00:06:57.625 --> 00:06:59.460
So the reason Russia is attacking

00:06:59.460 --> 00:07:01.129
so many different targets

00:07:01.129 --> 00:07:03.756
is they are trying to figure out where

00:07:03.756 --> 00:07:05.049
Ukraine is soft

00:07:05.049 --> 00:07:06.884
and where they have their defenses.

00:07:06.884 --> 00:07:08.219
And I think that's going to continue

00:07:08.219 --> 00:07:10.304
on for the next couple of days.

00:07:10.304 --> 00:07:12.014
And it just shows the importance

00:07:12.014 --> 00:07:13.641
