00:07:17.728 --> 00:07:20.857
more ammo and arms to Ukraine

00:07:20.857 --> 00:07:21.858
during this period of time.

00:07:21.858 --> 00:07:23.776
And this is a critical period.

00:07:23.776 --> 00:07:24.861
Lieutenant General Mark Hertling,

00:07:24.861 --> 00:07:25.945
always appreciate your insight.

